                        collateral and will enable borrowers to take leverage on
                        their ADA or other supported assets.
                    </p>
                    <% let btn = {width: 166, name: "Coming Soon"} %>
                    <%- include('../../../components/button.ejs', {btn: btn}) %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
